.Dd @RELEASE_DATE@
.Os
.Dt PLABUN 1
.Sh NAME
.Nm plabun
.Nd plot abundances computed by astrochem using hdf5 output file
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Ar option
.Ar file.h5
.Ar specie1
.Op Ar specie2 ...
.\"
.\" Description
.\"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
is a 
.Xr python 1
script to plot the abundances computed by
.Xr astrochem 1
vs. time
.\"
.\" Options
.\"
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width flag
.It Cm -h, --help
Display help text.
.It Cm -V, --version
Display plabun version information.
.It Cm -o Ar file , Cm --output= Ar file
Create a PostScript file.
.It Cm -c Ar cell-number , Cm --cell= Ar cell-number
Set the cell number. Default is 0.
.It Cm -x Ar xmin,xmax , Cm --xrange= Ar xmin,xmax
Set the x axis range
.It Cm -y Ar ymin,ymax , Cm --yrange= Ar ymin,ymax
Set the y axis range
.It Cm -l, --legacy
Read files in the legacy format (.abun)
.El
